The paper focuses on the development of a system for exploratory analysis of document collections using machine learning and natural language processing techniques. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Deep Learning (cs.DL), and Machine Learning (cs.LG). However, given the emphasis on tagging and faceted browsing, cs.IR is the most likely sub-category.
